Halalan
Version 0.1.2
http://sourceforge.net/projects/halalan
Copyright (C) 2006 UP Linux Users' Group


VERSION FEATURES:

This is the version used in the University of the Philippines Diliman Department of Computer Science Batch Representatives Election.  Initial SMS implementation is included.  This is intended for developers interested in helping the project.


INSTALLATION:

See INSTALL


PURPOSE:

Halalan is an open source web and mobile voting system specifically designed for the University of the Philippines student elections but can be used in other elections with little or no modifications.


DOCUMENT FORMAT:

The formating of files under docs/ are copied from the documents of PHP Timeclock http://timeclock.sourceforge.net.


